content.description:
This three bolt route stands out on great looking rock on the Spearman Ranch side of the Rock Garden (a few climbs to the left of

Team Geritol

).  The first bolt is about 15' off the ground, but there is a ledge you can scramble up to and make an easy first clip.  The climbing is tricky, so use your feet as the hueco pockets aren't as positive as they look from the ground.
